vibe mathz

fr fr Minimal mathz module with only essential functions for test suite

fr fr Absolute Value Functions - minimal and safe
slay abs_normie(x normie) normie {
    lowkey x < 0 {
        damn -x
    }
    damn x
}

slay abs_meal(x meal) meal {
    lowkey x < 0.0 {
        damn -x
    }
    damn x
}
